title: Willits Municipal Airport
text: Willits Municipal Airport , also known as Ells Field, is a public <a href="airport">airport</a> located three miles (4.6 km) northwest of <a href="Willits%2C%20California">Willits</a>, serving <a href="Mendocino%20County%2C%20California">Mendocino County</a>, <a href="California">California</a>, <a href="United%20States">USA</a>. This <a href="general%20aviation">general aviation</a> airport covers 75 <a href="acre">acre</a>s and has one <a href="runway">runway</a>.
